---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="NoLogin Verified Badge"
  description="What is NoLogin Verified? Learn about the badge that certifies tools work without login."
>
  <script type="application/ld+json" set:html={JSON.stringify({
    '@context': 'https://schema.org',
    '@type': 'FAQPage',
    mainEntity: [
      {
        '@type': 'Question',
        name: 'What is NoLogin Verified?',
        acceptedAnswer: {
          '@type': 'Answer',
          text: 'NoLogin Verified is a digital trust certificate issued by NoLoginTools.org to web applications that have been manually audited. It guarantees that the core functionality of a tool is accessible without sign-up or login.',
        },
      },
      {
        '@type': 'Question',
        name: 'What does the NoLogin Verified badge mean?',
        acceptedAnswer: {
          '@type': 'Answer',
          text: 'The badge means the tool has been manually reviewed and confirmed to provide its core functionality without requiring users to create an account or log in. It signals a commitment to privacy and frictionless access.',
        },
      },
      {
        '@type': 'Question',
        name: 'How can I get the NoLogin Verified badge for my tool?',
        acceptedAnswer: {
          '@type': 'Answer',
          text: 'Submit your tool at nologin.tools/submit. Our team will manually review it within approximately 48 hours. If approved, you will receive a unique badge embed code to display on your site.',
        },
      },
      {
        '@type': 'Question',
        name: 'Does displaying the badge affect my ranking on nologin.tools?',
        acceptedAnswer: {
          '@type': 'Answer',
          text: 'Yes. Tools that display the NoLogin Verified SVG badge on their site receive +10 ranking points, while those using a meta tag or link get +5 points. Tools without a badge receive no bonus.',
        },
      },
    ],
  })} />

  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 py-16 sm:py-24">
    <!-- Hero -->
    <div class="text-center mb-16">
      <div class="mb-8">
        <img
          src="/badge.svg"
          alt="NoLogin Verified"
          class="w-48 mx-auto"
        />
      </div>
      <h1 class="text-2xl font-bold tracking-tight text-neutral-900 mb-4">
        The <span class="text-green-600">NoLogin</span> Standard
      </h1>
      <p class="text-base text-neutral-500 max-w-2xl mx-auto leading-relaxed">
        We're on a mission to celebrate tools that let you work instantly — without the friction of accounts, passwords, or data harvesting.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- What is NoLogin Verified? -->
    <div class="border-b pb-8 mb-8">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-neutral-900 mb-4">What is NoLogin Verified?</h2>
      <div class="space-y-3 text-neutral-600 leading-relaxed">
        <p>
          It is a <span class="text-neutral-900 font-semibold">digital trust certificate</span> issued by <a href="https://nologintools.org" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-green-600 hover:text-green-700 font-semibold transition-colors">NoLoginTools.org</a> to web applications that have been manually audited by our team.
        </p>
        <p>
          When a tool displays this badge, it serves as a guarantee that the **core functionality** promised by the tool is accessible to any user immediately, without the requirement to sign up, log in, or provide personal credentials.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Three-column grid -->
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-4 mb-16">
      <div class="border rounded-lg p-4 text-center">
        <h3 class="font-bold text-neutral-900 mb-1 text-sm">No Accounts</h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-neutral-500">Skip the "Sign Up" button. Just open the URL and start creating immediately.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="border rounded-lg p-4 text-center">
        <h3 class="font-bold text-neutral-900 mb-1 text-sm">Privacy First</h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-neutral-500">Your data stays with you. No email lists, no tracking, no unwanted marketing.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="border rounded-lg p-4 text-center">
        <h3 class="font-bold text-neutral-900 mb-1 text-sm">Instant Value</h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-neutral-500">Zero friction means you get your task done 10x faster than traditional tools.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="space-y-12">
      <!-- Two Column Layout for Users/Creators -->
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
        <!-- For Users -->
        <section class="border rounded-lg p-6">
          <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-neutral-900 mb-4 flex items-center gap-2">
            <span class="w-6 h-6 rounded bg-green-100 flex items-center justify-center text-green-600 text-xs font-bold">U</span>
            The Verified Seal
          </h2>
          <p class="text-sm text-neutral-600 leading-relaxed mb-4">
            When you see the <span class="text-green-600 font-semibold">NoLogin Verified</span> badge, you can trust that:
          </p>
          <ul class="space-y-3">
            {[
              { title: "Manual Review", desc: "Every tool is individually tested by our verification team." },
              { title: "Core Task Verified", desc: "We confirm the main utility is accessible without sign-up." },
              { title: "Health Monitoring", desc: "We track tool availability daily to ensure they stay accessible." },
              { title: "Digital Preservation", desc: "Verified tools are archived to ensure long-term transparency." }
            ].map(item => (
              <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
                <svg class="mt-0.5 shrink-0 text-green-500" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor">
                  <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
                </svg>
                <div>
                  <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-neutral-900">{item.title}</p>
                  <p class="text-xs text-neutral-500 mt-0.5 leading-relaxed">{item.desc}</p>
                </div>
              </li>
            ))}
          </ul>
        </section>

        <!-- For Creators -->
        <section class="border rounded-lg p-6">
          <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-neutral-900 mb-4 flex items-center gap-2">
            <span class="w-6 h-6 rounded bg-blue-100 flex items-center justify-center text-blue-600 text-xs font-bold">C</span>
            Join the Directory
          </h2>
          <p class="text-sm text-neutral-600 leading-relaxed mb-6">
            Building a privacy-first tool? Get recognized for your commitment to a registration-free experience.
          </p>
          <div class="space-y-4">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
               <div class="w-8 h-8 rounded bg-neutral-50 border border-neutral-200 flex items-center justify-center text-neutral-400 text-sm font-bold">1</div>
               <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-neutral-700">Submit your tool details</p>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
               <div class="w-8 h-8 rounded bg-neutral-50 border border-neutral-200 flex items-center justify-center text-neutral-400 text-sm font-bold">2</div>
               <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-neutral-700">Verification review (~48h)</p>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
               <div class="w-8 h-8 rounded bg-neutral-50 border border-neutral-200 flex items-center justify-center text-neutral-400 text-sm font-bold">3</div>
               <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-neutral-700">Approval & Directory listing</p>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
               <div class="w-8 h-8 rounded bg-neutral-50 border border-neutral-200 flex items-center justify-center text-neutral-400 text-sm font-bold">4</div>
               <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-neutral-700">Get your unique badge code</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </section>
      </div>

      <!-- Ranking Boost -->
      <section class="border-t pt-8 mt-8">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-neutral-900 mb-2 text-center">Ranking Boost</h2>
        <p class="text-neutral-500 mb-8 max-w-xl mx-auto text-center text-sm">
          Tools that display our badge on their site receive a ranking boost in the nologin.tools directory.
        </p>

        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-3 gap-4">
          <div class="p-5 border rounded-lg text-center">
            <p class="font-bold text-neutral-900 mb-1 text-sm uppercase tracking-tight">SVG Badge</p>
            <p class="text-green-600 font-bold text-2xl">+10</p>
            <p class="text-[10px] text-neutral-400 uppercase tracking-widest font-semibold mt-1">Rank Points</p>
          </div>

          <div class="p-5 border rounded-lg text-center">
            <p class="font-bold text-neutral-900 mb-1 text-sm uppercase tracking-tight">Meta / Link</p>
            <p class="text-blue-600 font-bold text-2xl">+5</p>
            <p class="text-[10px] text-neutral-400 uppercase tracking-widest font-semibold mt-1">Rank Points</p>
          </div>

          <div class="p-5 border rounded-lg text-center">
            <p class="font-bold text-neutral-900 mb-1 text-sm uppercase tracking-tight">No Badge</p>
            <p class="text-neutral-400 font-bold text-2xl">0</p>
            <p class="text-[10px] text-neutral-400 uppercase tracking-widest font-semibold mt-1">Rank Points</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- CTA -->
      <div class="text-center pt-4">
        <a href="/submit" class="btn-minimal-primary">
          Submit Your Tool
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
